CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 9, 1958, pg. A15, reads: "Having Fun at Frog's Dance were these localites, left to right: Mr. and Mrs. James Goode, Mrs. Leon Waddy, Vivian Scott Hale, Evelyn and Morgan Thomas, the Walter Hales, Dr. Leon Waddy and the William Crawfords. - Teenie Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait, from left: Louisa Jeffries Webster Goode, James Goode, Mable Waddy, Vivian Scott Hale, Evelyn Thomas, Morgan Thomas, Mr. and Mrs. Walter Hale, Dr. Leon Waddy, Pauline Lowry Crawford, and William Crawford, gathered around banquet table for FROGS event, Gateway Plaza
